{
  "video_id": "YY1ERM-NIBY",
  "title": "Why being respectful to your coworkers is good for business | Christine Porath",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12927.0,
      "end_time": 14642.0,
      "text": "Who do you want to be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15317.0,
      "end_time": 17295.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a simple question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17319.0,
      "end_time": 19700.0,
      "text": "and whether you know it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19950.0,
      "end_time": 22360.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re answering it every day through your actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22971.0,
      "end_time": 27444.0,
      "text": "This one question will define your professional success"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27468.0,
      "end_time": 29492.0,
      "text": "more than any other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29516.0,
      "end_time": 33497.0,
      "text": "because how you show up and treat people means everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34116.0,
      "end_time": 38318.0,
      "text": "Either you lift people up by respecting them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38342.0,
      "end_time": 42402.0,
      "text": "making them feel valued, appreciated and heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43290.0,
      "end_time": 47970.0,
      "text": "or you hold people down by making them feel small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47994.0,
      "end_time": 51872.0,
      "text": "insulted, disregarded or excluded."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52314.0,
      "end_time": 55885.0,
      "text": "And who you choose to be means everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56631.0,
      "end_time": 59604.0,
      "text": "I study the effects of incivility on people."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59628.0,
      "end_time": 61313.0,
      "text": "What is incivility?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61337.0,
      "end_time": 63285.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s disrespect or rudeness."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63620.0,
      "end_time": 65982.0,
      "text": "It includes a lot of different behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66600.0,
      "end_time": 68360.0,
      "text": "from mocking or belittling someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68384.0,
      "end_time": 70923.0,
      "text": "to teasing people in ways that sting"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70947.0,
      "end_time": 72806.0,
      "text": "to telling offensive jokes"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72830.0,
      "end_time": 74639.0,
      "text": "to texting in meetings."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74663.0,
      "end_time": 79570.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s uncivil to one person may be absolutely fine to another."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79414.0,
      "end_time": 82820.0,
      "text": "Take texting while someone&#39;s speaking to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82106.0,
      "end_time": 84268.0,
      "text": "Some of us may find it rude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84292.0,
      "end_time": 87147.0,
      "text": "others may think it&#39;s absolutely civil."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87171.0,
      "end_time": 88831.0,
      "text": "So it really depends."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88855.0,
      "end_time": 93908.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all in the eyes of the beholder and whether that person felt disrespected."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94748.0,
      "end_time": 97537.0,
      "text": "We may not mean to make someone feel that way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97561.0,
      "end_time": 100498.0,
      "text": "but when we do, it has consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101736.0,
      "end_time": 103630.0,
      "text": "Over 22 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103654.0,
      "end_time": 107161.0,
      "text": "I vividly recall walking into this stuffy hospital room."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107901.0,
      "end_time": 113919.0,
      "text": "It was heartbreaking to see my dad, this strong, athletic, energetic guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113943.0,
      "end_time": 117627.0,
      "text": "lying in the bed with electrodes strapped to his bare chest."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118548.0,
      "end_time": 121374.0,
      "text": "What put him there was work-related stress."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122330.0,
      "end_time": 124510.0,
      "text": "For over a decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124750.0,
      "end_time": 127435.0,
      "text": "he suffered an uncivil boss."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129244.0,
      "end_time": 133556.0,
      "text": "And for me, I thought he was just an outlier at that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134382.0,
      "end_time": 136868.0,
      "text": "But just a couple years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136892.0,
      "end_time": 139781.0,
      "text": "I witnessed and experienced a lot of incivility"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139806.0,
      "end_time": 141520.0,
      "text": "in my first job out of college."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142441.0,
      "end_time": 144862.0,
      "text": "I spent a year going to work every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144886.0,
      "end_time": 147227.0,
      "text": "and hearing things from coworkers like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147251.0,
      "end_time": 150469.0,
      "text": "\"Are you an idiot? That&#39;s not how it&#39;s done,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150493.0,
      "end_time": 153916.0,
      "text": "and, \"If I wanted your opinion, I&#39;d ask.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155250.0,
      "end_time": 157838.0,
      "text": "So I did the natural thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 157862.0,
      "end_time": 161845.0,
      "text": "I quit, and I went back to grad school to study the effects of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162437.0,
      "end_time": 164701.0,
      "text": "There, I met Christine Pearson."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165218.0,
      "end_time": 168869.0,
      "text": "And she had a theory that small, uncivil actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168894.0,
      "end_time": 171282.0,
      "text": "can lead to much bigger problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171306.0,
      "end_time": 173408.0,
      "text": "like aggression and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173908.0,
      "end_time": 177896.0,
      "text": "We believed that incivility affected performance and the bottom line."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 177920.0,
      "end_time": 181661.0,
      "text": "So we launched a study, and what we found was eye-opening."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 182383.0,
      "end_time": 185530.0,
      "text": "We sent a survey to business school alumni"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185770.0,
      "end_time": 187468.0,
      "text": "working in all different organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 187492.0,
      "end_time": 189966.0,
      "text": "We asked them to write a few sentences"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189991.0,
      "end_time": 193500.0,
      "text": "about one experience where they were treated rudely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 193290.0,
      "end_time": 195619.0,
      "text": "disrespectfully or insensitively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 195643.0,
      "end_time": 198629.0,
      "text": "and to answer questions about how they reacted."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 200621.0,
      "end_time": 204393.0,
      "text": "One person told us about a boss that made insulting statements like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204417.0,
      "end_time": 206680.0,
      "text": "\"That&#39;s kindergartner&#39;s work,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206772.0,
      "end_time": 211278.0,
      "text": "and another tore up someone&#39;s work in front of the entire team."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211751.0,
      "end_time": 216156.0,
      "text": "And what we found is that incivility made people less motivated:"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 216180.0,
      "end_time": 219419.0,
      "text": "66 percent cut back work efforts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 219443.0,
      "end_time": 222462.0,
      "text": "80 percent lost time worrying about what happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222486.0,
      "end_time": 225482.0,
      "text": "and 12 percent left their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226506.0,
      "end_time": 230177.0,
      "text": "And after we published these results, two things happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 230201.0,
      "end_time": 232892.0,
      "text": "One, we got calls from organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 233503.0,
      "end_time": 235280.0,
      "text": "Cisco read about these numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 235305.0,
      "end_time": 239849.0,
      "text": "took just a few of these and estimated, conservatively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 239873.0,
      "end_time": 243112.0,
      "text": "that incivility was costing them 12 million dollars a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 243961.0,
      "end_time": 248701.0,
      "text": "The second thing that happened was, we heard from others in our academic field"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248725.0,
      "end_time": 253369.0,
      "text": "who said, \"Well, people are reporting this, but how can you really show it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253393.0,
      "end_time": 255931.0,
      "text": "Does people&#39;s performance really suffer?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 256711.0,
      "end_time": 258593.0,
      "text": "I was curious about that, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259459.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263288.0,
      "text": "With Amir Erez, I compared those that experienced incivility"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 263312.0,
      "end_time": 266880.0,
      "text": "to those that didn&#39;t experience incivility."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266112.0,
      "end_time": 269791.0,
      "text": "And what we found is that those that experience incivility"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 269815.0,
      "end_time": 272468.0,
      "text": "do actually function much worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273571.0,
      "end_time": 275983.0,
      "text": "\"OK,\" you may say. \"This makes sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 276700.0,
      "end_time": 279362.0,
      "text": "After all, it&#39;s natural that their performance suffers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280394.0,
      "end_time": 283567.0,
      "text": "But what about if you&#39;re not the one who experiences it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284202.0,
      "end_time": 286284.0,
      "text": "What if you just see or hear it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 286855.0,
      "end_time": 288356.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re a witness."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 288380.0,
      "end_time": 290920.0,
      "text": "We wondered if it affected witnesses, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 291809.0,
      "end_time": 293800.0,
      "text": "So we conducted studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 293104.0,
      "end_time": 296700.0,
      "text": "where five participants would witness an experimenter act rudely"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 296725.0,
      "end_time": 299178.0,
      "text": "to someone who arrived late to the study."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 299678.0,
      "end_time": 302382.0,
      "text": "The experimenter said, \"What is it with you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 302406.0,
      "end_time": 304684.0,
      "text": "You arrive late, you&#39;re irresponsible."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304708.0,
      "end_time": 307944.0,
      "text": "Look at you! How do you expect to hold a job in the real world?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 311269.0,
      "text": "And in another study in a small group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311293.0,
      "end_time": 314652.0,
      "text": "we tested the effects of a peer insulting a group member."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 315442.0,
      "end_time": 317825.0,
      "text": "Now, what we found was really interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317849.0,
      "end_time": 320517.0,
      "text": "because witnesses&#39; performance decreased, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320541.0,
      "end_time": 324311.0,
      "text": "and not just marginally, quite significantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 326159.0,
      "end_time": 328250.0,
      "text": "Incivility is a bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 328576.0,
      "end_time": 330197.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s contagious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 330221.0,
      "end_time": 334620.0,
      "text": "and we become carriers of it just by being around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334525.0,
      "end_time": 337111.0,
      "text": "And this isn&#39;t confined to the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 337136.0,
      "end_time": 339657.0,
      "text": "We can catch this virus anywhere --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 339681.0,
      "end_time": 344133.0,
      "text": "at home, online, in schools and in our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 345690.0,
      "end_time": 349588.0,
      "text": "It affects our emotions, our motivation, our performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 349612.0,
      "end_time": 350975.0,
      "text": "and how we treat others."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 351531.0,
      "end_time": 355314.0,
      "text": "It even affects our attention and can take some of our brainpower."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 356283.0,
      "end_time": 359859.0,
      "text": "And this happens not only if we experience incivility"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 359883.0,
      "end_time": 361428.0,
      "text": "or we witness it."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 361452.0,
      "end_time": 365267.0,
      "text": "It can happen even if we just see or read rude words."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 366290.0,
      "end_time": 368580.0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example of what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 369424.0,
      "end_time": 372522.0,
      "text": "To test this, we gave people combinations of words"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 372547.0,
      "end_time": 374280.0,
      "text": "to use to make a sentence."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 374591.0,
      "end_time": 376318.0,
      "text": "But we were very sneaky."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376850.0,
      "end_time": 382333.0,
      "text": "Half the participants got a list with 15 words used to trigger rudeness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 382357.0,
      "end_time": 386821.0,
      "text": "impolitely, interrupt, obnoxious, bother."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 387414.0,
      "end_time": 390128.0,
      "text": "Half the participants received a list of words"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390153.0,
      "end_time": 392339.0,
      "text": "with none of these rude triggers."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392950.0,
      "end_time": 395714.0,
      "text": "And what we found was really surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 395738.0,
      "end_time": 398138.0,
      "text": "because the people who got the rude words"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398162.0,
      "end_time": 402472.0,
      "text": "were five times more likely to miss information right in front of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402497.0,
      "end_time": 403854.0,
      "text": "on the computer screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 404671.0,
      "end_time": 406741.0,
      "text": "And as we continued this research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 406765.0,
      "end_time": 410121.0,
      "text": "what we found is that those that read the rude words"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 410145.0,
      "end_time": 412104.0,
      "text": "took longer to make decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 412129.0,
      "end_time": 413873.0,
      "text": "to record their decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 413897.0,
      "end_time": 416414.0,
      "text": "and they made significantly more errors."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 417263.0,
      "end_time": 418974.0,
      "text": "This can be a big deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 418999.0,
      "end_time": 422292.0,
      "text": "especially when it comes to life-and-death situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 422887.0,
      "end_time": 426646.0,
      "text": "Steve, a physician, told me about a doctor that he worked with"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 426670.0,
      "end_time": 428396.0,
      "text": "who was never very respectful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 428420.0,
      "end_time": 430846.0,
      "text": "especially to junior staff and nurses."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 431381.0,
      "end_time": 434784.0,
      "text": "But Steve told me about this one particular interaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 434808.0,
      "end_time": 437552.0,
      "text": "where this doctor shouted at a medical team."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 438544.0,
      "end_time": 440337.0,
      "text": "Right after the interaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 440361.0,
      "end_time": 443908.0,
      "text": "the team gave the wrong dosage of medication to their patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 445289.0,
      "end_time": 449120.0,
      "text": "Steve said the information was right there on the chart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 449144.0,
      "end_time": 452387.0,
      "text": "but somehow everyone on the team missed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 453307.0,
      "end_time": 456960.0,
      "text": "He said they lacked the attention or awareness to take it into account."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 457698.0,
      "end_time": 459322.0,
      "text": "Simple mistake, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 459803.0,
      "end_time": 461304.0,
      "text": "Well, that patient died."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 462462.0,
      "end_time": 465640.0,
      "text": "Researchers in Israel have actually shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 465664.0,
      "end_time": 468149.0,
      "text": "that medical teams exposed to rudeness"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 468173.0,
      "end_time": 471606.0,
      "text": "perform worse not only in all their diagnostics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 471630.0,
      "end_time": 473756.0,
      "text": "but in all the procedures they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 474607.0,
      "end_time": 477775.0,
      "text": "This was mainly because the teams exposed to rudeness"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 477799.0,
      "end_time": 480227.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t share information as readily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 480251.0,
      "end_time": 483104.0,
      "text": "and they stopped seeking help from their teammates."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 483128.0,
      "end_time": 487100.0,
      "text": "And I see this not only in medicine but in all industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 488581.0,
      "end_time": 491635.0,
      "text": "So if incivility has such a huge cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 491659.0,
      "end_time": 493668.0,
      "text": "why do we still see so much of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 494636.0,
      "end_time": 497560.0,
      "text": "I was curious, so we surveyed people about this, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 498680.0,
      "end_time": 500933.0,
      "text": "The number one reason is stress."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 500958.0,
      "end_time": 502669.0,
      "text": "People feel overwhelmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503849.0,
      "end_time": 506527.0,
      "text": "The other reason that people are not more civil"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 506552.0,
      "end_time": 509326.0,
      "text": "is because they&#39;re skeptical and even concerned"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 509350.0,
      "end_time": 511980.0,
      "text": "about being civil or appearing nice."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 512400.0,
      "end_time": 514527.0,
      "text": "They believe they&#39;ll appear less leader-like."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 514551.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517487.00000000006,
      "text": "They wonder: Do nice guys finish last?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 518419.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520975.99999999994,
      "text": "Or in other words: Do jerks get ahead?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 521000.0,
      "end_time": 522303.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 523870.0,
      "end_time": 524576.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easy to think so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 524600.0,
      "end_time": 527525.0,
      "text": "especially when we see a few prominent examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 527549.0,
      "end_time": 529515.0,
      "text": "that dominate the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 530466.0,
      "end_time": 533253.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out, in the long run, they don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 534630.0,
      "end_time": 538390.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s really rich research on this by Morgan McCall and Michael Lombardo"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 538630.0,
      "end_time": 540702.0,
      "text": "when they were at the Center for Creative Leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 540726.0,
      "end_time": 545535.0,
      "text": "They found that the number one reason tied to executive failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 545559.0,
      "end_time": 549198.0,
      "text": "was an insensitive, abrasive or bullying style."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 550428.0,
      "end_time": 554794.0,
      "text": "There will always be some outliers that succeed despite their incivility."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 554818.0,
      "end_time": 556381.0,
      "text": "Sooner or later, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 556405.0,
      "end_time": 559424.0,
      "text": "most uncivil people sabotage their success."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 560217.0,
      "end_time": 562210.0,
      "text": "For example, with uncivil executives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 562234.0,
      "end_time": 565282.0,
      "text": "it comes back to hurt them when they&#39;re in a place of weakness"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 565306.0,
      "end_time": 566723.0,
      "text": "or they need something."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 566747.0,
      "end_time": 568532.0,
      "text": "People won&#39;t have their backs."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 569795.0,
      "end_time": 571716.0,
      "text": "But what about nice guys?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 571740.0,
      "end_time": 573389.0,
      "text": "Does civility pay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 573413.0,
      "end_time": 575170.0,
      "text": "Yes, it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 575853.0,
      "end_time": 580263.0,
      "text": "And being civil doesn&#39;t just mean that you&#39;re not a jerk."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 580288.0,
      "end_time": 584152.0,
      "text": "Not holding someone down isn&#39;t the same as lifting them up."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 584605.0,
      "end_time": 587840.0,
      "text": "Being truly civil means doing the small things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 587864.0,
      "end_time": 590914.0,
      "text": "like smiling and saying hello in the hallway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 590938.0,
      "end_time": 593821.0,
      "text": "listening fully when someone&#39;s speaking to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 596290.0,
      "text": "Now, you can have strong opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 596315.0,
      "end_time": 601334.0,
      "text": "disagree, have conflict or give negative feedback civilly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 601358.0,
      "end_time": 602846.0,
      "text": "with respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 602870.0,
      "end_time": 605282.0,
      "text": "Some people call it \"radical candor,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 605306.0,
      "end_time": 606794.0,
      "text": "where you care personally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 606818.0,
      "end_time": 608589.0,
      "text": "but you challenge directly."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 609612.0,
      "end_time": 612250.0,
      "text": "So yes, civility pays."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612474.0,
      "end_time": 615369.0,
      "text": "In a biotechnology firm, colleagues and I found"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 615393.0,
      "end_time": 617468.0,
      "text": "that those that were seen as civil"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 617492.0,
      "end_time": 620128.0,
      "text": "were twice as likely to be viewed as leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 620153.0,
      "end_time": 622451.0,
      "text": "and they performed significantly better."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 623660.0,
      "end_time": 625430.0,
      "text": "Why does civility pay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 625670.0,
      "end_time": 629815.0,
      "text": "Because people see you as an important -- and a powerful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 629839.0,
      "end_time": 633542.0,
      "text": "unique combination of two key characteristics:"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 633566.0,
      "end_time": 636641.0,
      "text": "warm and competent, friendly and smart."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 637184.0,
      "end_time": 641684.0,
      "text": "In other words, being civil isn&#39;t just about motivating others."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641708.0,
      "end_time": 642968.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 643643.0,
      "end_time": 647150.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re civil, you&#39;re more likely to be seen as a leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 647174.0,
      "end_time": 650357.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll perform better, and you&#39;re seen as warm and competent."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 651722.0,
      "end_time": 655430.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s an even bigger story about how civility pays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 655454.0,
      "end_time": 659472.0,
      "text": "and it ties to one of the most important questions around leadership:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 660234.0,
      "end_time": 663120.0,
      "text": "What do people want most from their leaders?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663993.0,
      "end_time": 667706.0,
      "text": "We took data from over 20,000 employees around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 667730.0,
      "end_time": 669735.0,
      "text": "and we found the answer was simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 670933.0,
      "end_time": 672145.0,
      "text": "respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 672711.0,
      "end_time": 675917.0,
      "text": "Being treated with respect was more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 675941.0,
      "end_time": 678437.0,
      "text": "than recognition and appreciation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 678461.0,
      "end_time": 680160.0,
      "text": "useful feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 680400.0,
      "end_time": 681977.0,
      "text": "even opportunities for learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 682675.0,
      "end_time": 686382.0,
      "text": "Those that felt respected were healthier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 686406.0,
      "end_time": 687781.0,
      "text": "more focused,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 687805.0,
      "end_time": 690310.0,
      "text": "more likely to stay with their organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 690335.0,
      "end_time": 692373.0,
      "text": "and far more engaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 694123.0,
      "end_time": 695798.0,
      "text": "So where do you start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 696219.0,
      "end_time": 699739.0,
      "text": "How can you lift people up and make people feel respected?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 700411.0,
      "end_time": 703478.0,
      "text": "Well, the nice thing is, it doesn&#39;t require a huge shift."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 703977.0,
      "end_time": 706523.0,
      "text": "Small things can make a big difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 707108.0,
      "end_time": 709766.0,
      "text": "I found that thanking people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 709790.0,
      "end_time": 711256.0,
      "text": "sharing credit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 711280.0,
      "end_time": 713120.0,
      "text": "listening attentively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 713663.0,
      "end_time": 716920.0,
      "text": "humbly asking questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 716116.0,
      "end_time": 718831.0,
      "text": "acknowledging others and smiling"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 718855.0,
      "end_time": 720243.0,
      "text": "has an impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 721497.0,
      "end_time": 725232.0,
      "text": "Patrick Quinlan, former CEO of Ochsner Health [System],"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 725256.0,
      "end_time": 728113.0,
      "text": "told me about the effects of their 10-5 way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 728137.0,
      "end_time": 730395.0,
      "text": "where if you&#39;re within 10 feet of someone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 730419.0,
      "end_time": 733690.0,
      "text": "you make eye contact and smile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 733930.0,
      "end_time": 734765.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re within five feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 734789.0,
      "end_time": 736820.0,
      "text": "you say hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 736721.0,
      "end_time": 739381.0,
      "text": "He explained that civility spread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 739405.0,
      "end_time": 741810.0,
      "text": "patient satisfaction scores rose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 741835.0,
      "end_time": 743731.0,
      "text": "as did patient referrals."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 744916.0,
      "end_time": 749212.0,
      "text": "Civility and respect can be used to boost an organization&#39;s performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 749808.0,
      "end_time": 755556.0,
      "text": "When my friend Doug Conant took over as CEO of Campbell&#39;s Soup Company in 2001,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 755580.0,
      "end_time": 758507.0,
      "text": "the company&#39;s market share had just dropped in half."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 758531.0,
      "end_time": 760205.0,
      "text": "Sales were declining,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 760230.0,
      "end_time": 762839.0,
      "text": "lots of people had just been laid off."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 762863.0,
      "end_time": 766687.0,
      "text": "A Gallup manager said it was the least engaged organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 766711.0,
      "end_time": 768570.0,
      "text": "that they had surveyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 768969.0,
      "end_time": 771894.0,
      "text": "And as Doug drove up to work his first day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 771918.0,
      "end_time": 775892.0,
      "text": "he noticed that the headquarters was surrounded by barbwire fence."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 776313.0,
      "end_time": 778894.0,
      "text": "There were guard towers in the parking lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 779775.0,
      "end_time": 783411.0,
      "text": "He said it looked like a minimum security prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 783436.0,
      "end_time": 785247.0,
      "text": "It felt toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 786771.0,
      "end_time": 789721.0,
      "text": "Within five years, Doug had turned things around."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 790182.0,
      "end_time": 793740.0,
      "text": "And within nine years, they were setting all-time performance records"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 793764.0,
      "end_time": 796719.0,
      "text": "and racking up awards, including best place to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 797449.0,
      "end_time": 798742.0,
      "text": "How did he do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 799416.0,
      "end_time": 801843.0,
      "text": "On day one, Doug told employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 801867.0,
      "end_time": 804534.0,
      "text": "that he was going to have high standards for performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 804558.0,
      "end_time": 806643.0,
      "text": "but they were going to do it with civility."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 806667.0,
      "end_time": 809893.0,
      "text": "He walked the talk, and he expected his leaders to."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 810805.0,
      "end_time": 815520.0,
      "text": "For Doug, it all came down to being tough-minded on standards"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 815544.0,
      "end_time": 817428.0,
      "text": "and tenderhearted with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 818119.0,
      "end_time": 821332.0,
      "text": "For him, he said it was all about these touch points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 821356.0,
      "end_time": 824563.0,
      "text": "or these daily interactions he had with employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 824587.0,
      "end_time": 828516.0,
      "text": "whether in the hallway, in the cafeteria or in meetings."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 829640.0,
      "end_time": 831742.0,
      "text": "And if he handled each touch point well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 831766.0,
      "end_time": 833894.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d make employees feel valued."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 835890.0,
      "end_time": 838604.0,
      "text": "Another way that Doug made employees feel valued"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 838628.0,
      "end_time": 841240.0,
      "text": "and showed them that he was paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 841480.0,
      "end_time": 846411.0,
      "text": "is that he handwrote over 30,000 thank-you notes to employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 846949.0,
      "end_time": 849290.0,
      "text": "And this set an example for other leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 850456.0,
      "end_time": 854141.0,
      "text": "Leaders have about 400 of these touch points a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 854165.0,
      "end_time": 857512.0,
      "text": "Most don&#39;t take long, less than two minutes each."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 857537.0,
      "end_time": 861844.0,
      "text": "The key is to be agile and mindful in each of these moments."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 862933.0,
      "end_time": 864663.0,
      "text": "Civility lifts people."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 865179.0,
      "end_time": 868664.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll get people to give more and function at their best"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 868688.0,
      "end_time": 869846.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;re civil."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 870528.0,
      "end_time": 873675.0,
      "text": "Incivility chips away at people and their performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 873699.0,
      "end_time": 875959.0,
      "text": "It robs people of their potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 875984.0,
      "end_time": 878900.0,
      "text": "even if they&#39;re just working around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 879100.0,
      "end_time": 883289.0,
      "text": "What I know from my research is that when we have more civil environments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 883313.0,
      "end_time": 888769.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re more productive, creative, helpful, happy and healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 889428.0,
      "end_time": 890868.0,
      "text": "We can do better."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 891479.0,
      "end_time": 894487.0,
      "text": "Each one of us can be more mindful"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 894511.0,
      "end_time": 898810.0,
      "text": "and can take actions to lift others up around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 898105.0,
      "end_time": 901393.0,
      "text": "at work, at home, online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 901417.0,
      "end_time": 902581.0,
      "text": "in schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 902605.0,
      "end_time": 904268.0,
      "text": "and in our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 904943.0,
      "end_time": 907391.0,
      "text": "In every interaction, think:"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 907829.0,
      "end_time": 909585.0,
      "text": "Who do you want to be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 910419.0,
      "end_time": 912932.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s put an end to incivility bug"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 912956.0,
      "end_time": 914920.0,
      "text": "and start spreading civility."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 915404.0,
      "end_time": 917647.0,
      "text": "After all, it pays."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 918219.0,
      "end_time": 919384.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 919408.0,
      "end_time": 921928.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}